{"tid":1235141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷緊工嘅你，返緊工嘅你，唔撚知做乜嘅你，請注意","createTime":"2019-06-17T05:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:08:19.000Z","uid":13754,"like":129,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d75ec05577001582d89c7b19f73004179a1301bb","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"要打持久戰，我哋要有健康嘅精神狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就好易做錯判斷，咁就變豬隊友嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜我哋吸收咗太多真嘅假嘅資訊，參加咗好多人行動，我哋需要休息一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好想喺度推動大家一齊，每日做靜觀（Mindfulness）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩係靜觀可以睇以下呢段片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-LHT_2sgMtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-LHT_2sgMtg&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=0c2d8ffd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-LHT_2sgMtg</a><br />\n<br />\n有研究指出，有持續進行靜觀習慣嘅人，大腦嘅灰質會增加，對人嘅同理心，耐性都會改善<br />\n<br />\n另外一個重點，係可以改善睡眠質素，令身體健康啲！<br />\n<br />\n呢度另外有一篇長文講靜觀<br />\n<a href=\"https://treehole.hk/靜觀-一文爲你解通/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftreehole.hk%2F%E9%9D%9C%E8%A7%80-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%88%B2%E4%BD%A0%E8%A7%A3%E9%80%9A%2F&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=8aadab71\" target=\"_blank\">https://treehole.hk/靜觀-一文爲你解通/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁靜觀點做呢？<br />\n其實真係好簡單<br />\n1. Set好Timer做1分鐘 (可以唔止1分鐘，但建議啱啱開始可以由每日1分鐘做起）<br />\n2. 坐好，雙手放喺大腿上<br />\n3. 合埋雙眼<br />\n4. 慢慢深呼吸，將注意力放喺<br />\n-- 鼻哥窿上面，感受下吸氣同呼氣鼻哥窿嘅感覺，或者<br />\n-- 腹部隆起同收縮嘅感覺<br />\n5. 重複4. 直到Timer響<br />\n<br />\n當你深呼吸嘅時候，可能會諗起好多嘢Side track你嘅注意力，但唔需要緊張，只要當你察覺到自己分咗心嘅時候，慢慢返返去鼻哥窿或者腹部嘅感覺就可以嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家趁而家放飯，留一分鐘時間畀自己做一做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94023e0e73272a80bfd08d3999a15b3f796319be","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa8f4c0059fcc0f2667bb31e2b17436c772d535b","tid":1235141,"uid":5523,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"有研究指出，有持續進行靜觀習慣嘅人，大腦嘅灰質會增加，對人嘅同理心，耐性都會改善<br />\n<br />\n毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76368360d29aceb1b5da58c66af0a5b5a4bc3c9","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa8f4c0059fcc0f2667bb31e2b17436c772d535b","tid":1235141,"uid":5523,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"有研究指出，有持續進行靜觀習慣嘅人，大腦嘅灰質會增加，對人嘅同理心，耐性都會改善<br />\n<br />\n毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"脫毒靠靜觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de13fb3cd911d3c1fc2fbfe1668bd42a2a3fba1","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"大家一齊做Mindfulness！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83d0c4029493074f03eef27246627627ace1ac3","tid":1235141,"uid":259759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n需要多d 軍師。"},{"pid":"389e9899232299922b8b9ff09a371b55e0eb4e16","tid":1235141,"uid":53811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"飯氣攻心去散下步都好<br />\n唔好掛住上連登"},{"pid":"0fd62b68671c030c283ad25caa08cfa8790bbbfd","tid":1235141,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuxS</a>"},{"pid":"aabb12232d80edd4620356d8d13c355ec5e371ee","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"389e9899232299922b8b9ff09a371b55e0eb4e16","tid":1235141,"uid":53811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"飯氣攻心去散下步都好<br />\n唔好掛住上連登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"呢位人兄講得啱，靜觀喺散步都可以做，我哋叫「靜心步行」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5YGGv6giL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di5YGGv6giL4&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=43d1e0a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5YGGv6giL4</a><br />\n<br />\n我個人建議先建立呼吸嘅習慣，再加埋呢個靜心步行，日日去練習就Perfect嘞!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2781bfd615de00ad05a3ba416a5cdf14b7ba437","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"成日都唔記得加［請廣傳]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a884985e036294963250adcee424b44a3f1feff","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"咁係我叫大家去做去練習，咁我又好簡單講下我做成點<br />\n<br />\n我係前年開始知呢樣嘢，嗰時我經歷咗一啲好大嘅問題，有啲Depress，個人情緒好唔穩定，同埋好容易焦慮<br />\n<br />\n當我去每日都預啲時間（我有空檔就做5分鐘）畀自己去深呼吸嘅時候，發覺個人會覺得平靜咗舒服咗，同埋會對啲事冇咁負面<br />\n<br />\n人一冇咁負面就開始識諗解決辦法，或者識得去接受啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n我都有去14年嘅雨革，嗰時我係好暴躁同好神經質，好容易會受人分化<br />\n<br />\n但今年我覺得自己係理性咗，對人有多咗同理心！<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友都話我同兩年前唔同咗好多，希望我哋都可以Be a better man!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb261154aaf87e404275d3153070e28766903af","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3eea06db8b80e2a0e8eebb358154c40a03d1bc99","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"做咗嘅請嚟推一推"},{"pid":"cc191aa662202f3fa0f523e27e0d1323b8133618","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f2faf2826c24db22722ffe8593688ec92ea199","tid":1235141,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85784add5c0e62c4f6f38e4f07bf772198e57424","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405a093263be11a1ec6ac64a673fc4bee7f4a516","tid":1235141,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"有冇AV推介 成個星期冇打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278f8f9e1c3b821d766a9e5c3001fee1d5434e6d","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"405a093263be11a1ec6ac64a673fc4bee7f4a516","tid":1235141,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"有冇AV推介 成個星期冇打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXSK676.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXSK676.png&h=0a91eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17fff73373a2cb8073858e586dfa5de2d41f6a37","tid":1235141,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"278f8f9e1c3b821d766a9e5c3001fee1d5434e6d","tid"